frc.robot.SuperClasses

Class BaseDriveHDrive

  • java.lang.Object
    • frc.robot.SuperClasses.BaseDrive
      • frc.robot.SuperClasses.BaseDriveHDrive

  • public abstract class BaseDriveHDrive
extends BaseDrive
    This code is meant to run an H-Drive in preperation for the 2020 offseason project as well as getting ready for if it's to be used in the future perhaps in the 2020 season. With this it needs some work as the main goal of this project is that we create a base class or set of base classes that can be used for multiple years. This can run an H-Drive, and has the pieces to be able to implement an H-Drive very easily in a PID controller.
